The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a method for modeling a distribution of possible outputs, which involves training a generator using a conditional generative modeling setting, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also explores different network architectures, which is a common topic in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
